of Nigeria's Head of State General Sani Abacha, and 13 others
have died in a plane crash in northern Nigeria, the News Agency
of Nigeria reported today.
</P>
<P>
The presidential jet, which was flying from Lagos to the
northern city of Kano, crashed on Wednesday night in a bush while
attempting to land at Malam Aminu Kano Airport.
</P>
