However, Kano State Administrator Mohammed Wase has
declared today and tomorrow as public holidays to enable people
to mourn and pray for the dead.
</P>
<P>
The 28-year-old Ibrahim, the first of Abacha's 10
children, is a businessman in Kano, hometown of the Abacha family.
</P>
<P>
There were four plane crashes in Nigeria in 1995 that caused
fatalities. 
