put questions to Scott, America's first black astronaut. The
discussion lasted about 30 minutes.
</P>
<P>
Ngubane initiated the event after meeting Scott in Washington
last year when he presented the astronaut with South Africa's
national flag. Scott took the flag with on his space mission and
will return it on a visit to South Africa later this year.
