<HEADLINE> Former Qatari Emir Arrives in Damascus </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DAMASCUS, January 18 (Xinhua) -- Former Qatari Emir Sheikh
Khalifa Bin Hamad Al Thani arrived in Damascus today on a private
visit to Syria.
</P>
<P>
He was greeted at Damascus International Airport by Syrian
President Hafez al-Assad.
</P>
<P>
According to an official Syrian source, President al-Assad held
a meeting with Sheikh Khalifa. But the details of the meeting were
not available.
</P>
