Al Thani, in a bloodless coup last June. Sheikh Hamad seized the
power when his father was abroad at the time.
</P>
<P>
The deposed emir, who toured Gulf states last month, has vowed
to return to his country and seize back his power.
</P>
<P>
Qatari Foreign Minister Sheikh Hamad Bin Jassem Bin Jaber Al
Thani said last month that the former emir "enjoys complete
freedom to travel" and his tour would not harm Qatar. 
