<TEXT>
<P>
SHANTOU, January 18 (Xinhua) -- With the help of the China
Travel Service Shantou Branch, an increasing number of overseas
Chinese are returning to Shantou, their home city, for a
sightseeing or business co-operation.
</P>
<P>
Sources of the visitors have been expanded to the United
States, France, Canada and Australia, from Thailand, Singapore and
Malaysia in the past.
</P>
