<HEADLINE> Shenzhen to Construct International Trading Plaza </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHENZHEN, January 18 (Xinhua) -- A Hong Kong company will
invest one billion Hong Kong dollars in constructing an
international trading plaza in the New Futian District here.
</P>
<P>
This is a new move to help Shenzhen, a window of China's reform
and opening-up, to build Futian into a modernized urban district
in the coming ten years.
</P>
