ended her good fortune in Grand Slam competitions.
</P>
<P>
She fell to Croatia's Iva Majoli in the fourth round of the
1995 French Open, went down to compatriot Nathalie Tauziat in the
second round at Wimbledon and was beaten in the third round at the
U.S. Open by American Amy Frazier. 
